title: See the video for Fall Out Boy and Demi Lovato's collaboration 'Irresistible' - Music
text: Fall Out Boy have unveiled the frankly weird, yet adorable, video for their team-up with Demi Lovato.The group re-released their American Beauty/American Psycho track 'Irresistible', this time with a Lovato twist.Featuring Internet star Doug the Pug, the video is a pug-ified version of the original video release and also sees Doug the Pug superimposed into previous Fall Out Boy efforts.Revealing the reasons behind the collaboration, the group said they felt 'Irresistible' could become "something else, something exciting, strange, beyond"."I think Demi Lovato has one of the most powerful voices today. So we worked through an afternoon and she just got it."Last week, Fall Out Boy also announced their 'Wintour', which will see the band embark on 20 new dates across America for 2016.Meanwhile, Lovato's new album Confident was released on Friday (October 16).
